data.description: This home has so much potential!  Lots of room inside and out, there is an enclosed patio for year round use, a large back yard with a deck overlooking it from the Master bedroom.  The lot is a great size, with a patio and a fire pit and chicken coop at the very back of the property. The layout of the home is split 2 bedrooms up and 2 down, has built-ins and plenty of storage.  Get creative and make this home as you wish.
